text: Gisela Raquel Mota Ocampo (13 March 1982 - 2 January 2016) was a Mexican politician. She was a member of the Party of the Democratic Revolution (PRD). She was the mayor of Temixco from 1 January 2016 until her death the next day. She was born in Temixco, Morelos. Mota Ocampo was shot dead at her home on 2 January 2016 in Pueblo Viejo, aged 33. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Mexican mayors Category:Murders by firearm Category:People from Morelos
